title: The Tina Challenge
description: Tina has prepared "The Tina Challenge" where Dave, Falen, Jenny, & Drake will compete in daily challenges and whoever has the lowest score at the end of the week has to do whatever's in They Mystery Box.  Monday's challenge is The Genre Game!
